      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLANKET GAME (4) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (25.87) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning five races. Has ability and can bounce back. PAW CALLIE (1) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Finished second (25.52) at this track last time making it two minors on end. Deserves a win and gets his chance. BLACK STATESMAN (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (25.73) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including six wins. Worth following up. PAW FABLE (3) did a good job to finish third last time out over 450m at this track (25.74) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
